Seether - Seether 2002-2013 (Greatest Hits)
Seether 2002-2013 is a two-disc compilation album by the South African rock band, Seether, released on October 29, 2013.
The first disc comprises the band's well-known songs and singles, while the second disc comprises a cover of Veruca Salt's song "Seether"
the song after which the band is named, two new studio tracks, plus unreleased demos, B-sides, and soundtrack songs.
